Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,微笑装备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也自然high
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得意忘形的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有预约时间(硬比出V手势)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.56,0:00:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女英雄驾到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.43,0:00:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽情的吃甜点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉烦人的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ThankYou! 挖到宝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.57,0:00:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招财猫招啊招(客人来吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.50,0:00:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定能进入你的内心殿堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦警报 (踩到地雷)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.81,0:00:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有点刺激才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算吃海苔时噎到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.62,0:00:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是盯著摄影机看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.92,0:00:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摆出明星架式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题V手势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.32,0:01:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使 Rock'n'Roll
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.19,0:01:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老套的乐园(啊摇摆摇摆)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.26,0:01:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋转的宇宙也在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火力全开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摇摇摆摆跳一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(啊摇摆摇摆)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.94,0:01:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都会变成天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.18,0:01:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长官，目前警戒区内没有发现可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续加强警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.13,0:01:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个被公布出去的话他们就完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是现在还不能安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们一定会使出什么招数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.64,0:01:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,职业杀手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，这个房间理论上应该只有你跟我进得来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么声音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.28,0:02:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从哪里发出来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在警戒区内的确没有发现可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为，自己看不见自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确认作战成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.81,0:02:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代号”00村上”继续前往执行下一个任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,试著接近新目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.38,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#17可洛洛俄罗斯红茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优被职业杀手盯上了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，据说那个杀手还是个狠角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是为什么杀手会盯上梅尔优?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就文件资料显示天使队留下了不少战绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中一部分的评价还写著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸运女孩梅尔优表现相当优异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.97,0:03:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算这样，他们打算对梅尔优做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是刚调派到整备课的凯萨·村上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後还请各位多多照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.58,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长得蛮帅的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么不懂的尽管问我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们好好相处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标，确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,职业杀手的五大誓词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一，为了计划成功要进行绵密的调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二，尽可能地接近目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确实掌握目标的长相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.85,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三，调查活动务必小心谨慎千万不可让目标发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如影随形的跟踪目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不让对方察觉观察目标的行踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当一切都掌握完毕之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是她的死期到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡事得秘密进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话多将招致失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这句话的意思是\N要让计划成功，必须秘密地进行对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.54,0:04:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问一下你刚才听到了什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.45,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是“她的死期到了”之前吗?还是之後?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.12,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉，知道我真正身份的人只有死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?可是我根本不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.59,0:04:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一个刚好路过的情报员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.59,0:04:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大，我可以告诉你很多这里的内幕情报喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在工作时习惯单独行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队的很多幕後八卦\N还有不可告人的羞耻事耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了达成任务请务必助我一臂之丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪，诺麦德你换对象了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为刚来不太习惯，所以找诺麦德指导一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.79,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队的脑袋变成我的了\N已经没什么好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就能尽情观察目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想光明正大的待在人家房间里对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有啦，我只是看你好像很开心．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽可能地接近目标是基本中的基本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点粗茶，请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然来拜访你，会不会让你感到困扰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是拜访还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是变态者的行为就有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我就不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是萨普利翁行星的健康茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.43,0:05:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，你好内行喔\N我最近迷上了健康食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我也是超喜欢健康食品的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还有这个喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯波朋行星的“如果如果的果实”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她真是个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还送了我一瓶维他命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我差点就毙了自己的情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情人?想不到你那么早就出人头地了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，原谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.33,0:06:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论我们多么相爱，只要接到命令我就得下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这是我的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你何必那么在意呢?对方根本对你没意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然来这里没多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我就要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，梅尔优你额头上开了一个洞耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难看死了，用0K绷贴住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就不会难看了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，这里有教即使头被打爆也能复活的咒语吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是这把枪有什么问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你们说，前些时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,枪果然没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.61,0:06:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?为什么突然会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦，快把鼻涕擦一擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村上先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,央优行星的那个到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有空的话，要不要来吃吃看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?那个梦幻极品吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，就是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，幸好我失手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以射杀这么棒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，这种人应该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用棒子槌死才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为．．．为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.91,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我使用的武器明明就没有问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.81,0:07:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，既然这样就用这种一颗就能毒死大象的剧毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.81,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，亚西贝行星的那个到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要试试看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的可以给我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总感觉身体变得健康多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是一场梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是一场恶梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.67,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不面对现实的话，凡事都无法前进喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前一片血红．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一招，进行下一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.26,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,华克中校那么努力的表现，至少也要嘉勉他一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，再这样下去会没完没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时候就需要这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.77,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的老师能为你指点迷津喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎来到我的咨询室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.44,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，把一切告诉老师让老师帮你做主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请把你少年时代的痛苦回忆告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师是专家，提起勇气说出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想想看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假的自由研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把根茎植物养烂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.67,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拿了一根葱去代替结果被大家取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要开枪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来气氛已经炒热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得与你的鸿沟越来越深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.67,0:09:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总是跟花鸟讲话个性有点内向的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，现在你需要的是登山健行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，就是登山健行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登山健行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?登山健行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.52,0:09:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我这次假期正准备去爬“御严厉山”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.13,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那座每年都传出山难的超危险的山吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.53,0:09:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是天助我也不．．．请让我跟你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这真是个绝佳的登山大好天气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊，一定会越来越健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.21,0:09:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我非得陪你们来不可呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想太多的话只会让自己接下来更痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么都不要想比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一定要做好万全准备杀了这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，你不要紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好戏还在後头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.67,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了?已经累了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有，只是有点头昏眼花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，我们继续赶路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.88,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.92,0:10:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山路总是有很多危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.79,0:10:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的没错大家要打起精神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，我就是这种打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么碰到那么多惨事她依然还活著?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再跟你说一次我觉得中校也是个狠角色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了，这里就是目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终於只剩我们两人了梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思来晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不晓得为什么弓箭突然像暴雨般地射过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你，我想要你的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你的人生给我好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这我办不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，这是不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优过度热衷於健康食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天突然暴毙死亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，这是可鲁波行星匹“耐耐本”健康食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有这个…  变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,够了，闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是一流的杀手盯上的猎物绝不让它逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.93,0:11:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,复活吧!梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很吵耶，你要搞到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.23,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说不定是个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始罗，剪刀石头布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡子绅士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有胡子我也有胡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明大家都有胡子为什么要互相憎恨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#18复仇姜汁汽水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.85,0:12:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?我最近很冷淡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这真是令人讶异啊，诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一向都很用心对人温柔又体贴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能请你确认一下你坐的地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.23,0:12:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇!诺麦德你什么时候跑来这里的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从你来这里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.37,0:12:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在的话就出声说一下嘛哇，好恶心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么好恶心?我是被害者耶．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们感情还是那么好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正走开啦，吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在要练习射击忙得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再继续吵的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心我让你脑袋开花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你是故意的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特对我施加的恶行最近越来越夸张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要向她好好报这个仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好感动喔，诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?你是乌丸千岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.91,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报仇，这两个字听起来实在太浪漫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是搞不懂年轻人的品味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让我帮你的忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.82,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让乌丸千岁尽点绵薄之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我能不能拜托你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直很想要一样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小事一桩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.58,0:13:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没跟我打声招呼你就想走过去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你在看什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本大爷的新手脚有那么稀奇吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很羡慕是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吓破胆了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你给我说说话啊，小佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这是干嘛!反对暴力!反对暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么说呢，你这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很碍眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能，怎么可能会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忙得要命，不要跟我讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.58,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我特地从仓库拿出来的遗失文明”手脚伸展君”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你终於得到盼望已久的手脚怎么还这样．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是手脚变长了而已根本一点都不强嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起来修行吧，诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,努力修行总有一天一定要复仇雪恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向佛特·修特伦复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我记住，佛特·修特伦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我在这里，在你後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了，诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无败的冠军此刻诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你，诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.79,0:15:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关於无败冠军的诞生请你发表一下感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来就是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特·修特伦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终於来到这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.58,0:15:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一来，我跟诺麦德就能成功复仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，这可不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫，马利普你们怎么会来这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.43,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想一个人赚大钱这你就大错特错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会赚得比你以前更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?千岁去了远方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.64,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，她好像去找能承受跟你练习的超级练拳对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.48,0:16:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以今後你身边的事就交给我们两个来处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你们两个这是干嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这次是夺冠比赛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定可以捞一笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我想说你一定很辛苦所以才．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.86,0:16:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以琐碎杂事都交给我们来处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要专心想比赛的事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们似乎另有目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，那就拜托你们罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.74,0:17:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，听说了吗?佛特好像是天使队的队长耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?在街上干架连赢200场的那个人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去跟诺麦德说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会一如往常的打得他跪地求饶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，我会让她知道谁才是真正的冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来她也蛮有自信的嘛(诺麦德一点都不可怕)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，诺麦德也调整到最佳状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也做好了万全的准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.88,0:17:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，但是为了慎重起见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比赛前双方的经纪人居然在这里密商
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这要是被媒体知道了他们一定会很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要跟我们谈什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我们怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没要你们做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.27,0:17:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要明天让佛特·修特伦身体出状况，不能好好比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於脚本就由你们来想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.88,0:18:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们准备了饮料给你喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒你的人一定是我觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.52,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，为什么她狗屎运那么好真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受够了(薄荷大小姐後援会聚会)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷大小姐，你到底怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天不展露笑容给我们看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那个臭佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.73,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身体状况一直不肯变差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然这样只能派军队直接攻击她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派军队攻击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回公司一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.92,0:19:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您今天回来得真早啊，司令官大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫特科大队出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标是天使队的佛特·修特伦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少废话，快给我出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底出了什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特受到军方的攻击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.72,0:19:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，不过这跟我们无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是，她如果不能来这个会场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胜利就会自动变成我们的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，这么密密麻麻一大堆到底是从哪里冒出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，到此为止吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你躺在那里干嘛还不快点站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德，你为什么要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒你的人一定是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先要解决这些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.76,0:21:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特与诺麦德都没来耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能来得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两个在跟军队打架耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.75,0:21:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，就算佛特他们很能打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也实在太鲁莽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.23,0:21:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我相信他们两人一定会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为．．．因为他们两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了在拳击场上对以往的恩怨做个了结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才拼命努力到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.77,0:21:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，开始吧，诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.57,0:22:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,榻榻米会燃烧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.77,0:22:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然会燃烧罗因为是用枯掉的稻草做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.94,0:22:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烧得超旺的(超萌的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.74,0:22:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上火灾了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.71,0:22:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真叫人受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.61,0:22:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吸到烟了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.61,0:22:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一种“来了”的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.81,0:22:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消防车吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.58,0:22:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得死了都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然消防车来了那就不要放弃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有榻榻米，我什么都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.45,0:22:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要这样说嘛其它还有很多东西没烧掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.39,0:22:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要气馁努力活下去就会有好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是幸福似神仙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.46,0:22:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么快就恢复啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.10,0:22:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,启动认真模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.56,0:22:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.36,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超very紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心儿呯呯跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.17,0:22:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私奔极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.91,0:23:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宛如软绵绵的蛋白霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心跳加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰淇淋派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吻了你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.65,0:23:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要溢出来的Jelly Beans
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.61,0:23:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥抱五彩缤纷的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将音调调至Pop
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.93,0:23:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚采收的新鲜鼓动
